*Schwarzenegger* announced his candidacy in the 2003 California recall election for Governor of California on the August 6 2003 episode of The Tonight Show with Jay Leno Schwarzenegger had the most name recognition in a crowded field of candidates, but he had never held public office and his political views were unknown to most Californians.
